tailing likes to spend his life in a bar.

12:10.731 --> 12:14.276
<i>There seems to be</i>
<i>no telling which way a life will go.</i>

12:14.359 --> 12:19.406
<i>In his younger days, my father played drums
in after-hours clubs all around Miami.</i>

12:19.489 --> 12:21.825
<i>A few times he even played New York.</i>

12:21.908 --> 12:24.244
<i>But when my mother</i>
<i>became pregnant with me,</i>

12:24.327 --> 12:29.458
<i>he gave it all up and settled into a
steady job as a crime scene detective.</i>

12:29.541 --> 12:32.002
<i>He said that the law was a straight line</i>

12:32.085 --> 12:37.002
<i>and that no man could stand firmly</i>
<i>with a foot on each side.</i>

12:55.066 --> 12:58.945
Yeah. Ned Bishop.
Fucking guy shot my fish.

12:59.029 --> 13:00.530
I asked the guy for a net.

13:00.614 --> 13:03.450
Next thing, he's firing
his fucking UZI into the water.

13:03.533 --> 13:06.286
Blew a hole like this
right through my fish.

13:06.369 --> 13:08.079
Who goes fishing without a net?

13:08.163 --> 13:10.957
Men, I'd like you to meet my wife.

13:11.041 --> 13:12.959
- This is Mary.
- Hello.

13:14.795 --> 13:17.756
I hate to bust up the little party
you gentlemen have going here,

13:17.839 --> 13:20.801
but I came to see you, Ryder.

13:20.884 --> 13:23.553
So rather than have you drag
yourself out in the daylight,

13:23.637 --> 13:26.056
I figured I'd grab you here tonight.

13:26.139 --> 13:27.889
So if you don't mind.

14:00.757 --> 14:03.718
An officer doesn't just lose his gun

14:03.802 --> 14:06.346
any more than
he just looses his hand.

14:06.429 --> 14:08.849
His weapon
is an extension of his body.

14:08.932 --> 14:10.725
Now I may be a little
idealistic here, Ryder,

14:10.809 --> 14:14.688
but I'd like to think that an officer,
if he did lose his gun-

14:14.771 --> 14:18.316
an officer, that is, who's been in the
department for some 30-odd years-

14:18.400 --> 14:22.237
that he might, just might
have a small sliver of recall

14:22.320 --> 14:24.737
as to the where and the when.

14:25.907 --> 14:28.285
I'm putting you on
a week's suspension, Ryder.

14:28.368 --> 14:31.872
