be assigned to investigate the situation.

14:31.955 --> 14:34.455
I think I can find my own gun.

15:06.239 --> 15:08.909
Man, I could shoot my way
right out of here.

15:08.992 --> 15:11.620
Come on, Lee, they're not
exactly holding you hostage.

15:11.703 --> 15:13.246
