15:13.330 --> 15:16.666
My grandmother keeps running in and
out of here with her tape measure.

15:16.750 --> 15:19.250
She's gonna give you the boot?

15:21.963 --> 15:24.257
I've been in this room my whole life.

15:24.341 --> 15:27.552
