every time the wind changes direction.

18:32.362 --> 18:33.988
How's Shelley doing?

18:34.072 --> 18:37.784
She's good. Been seeing some boy
from over at the junior college.

18:37.867 --> 18:39.911
<i>You see them everywhere you look.</i>

18:39.994 --> 18:42.914
<i>And I don't know why</i>
<i>I never thought of it before,</i>

18:42.997 --> 18:45.416
<i>but one day I just started wondering-</i>

18:45.500 --> 18:47.961
<i>where are all</i>
<i>those highways heading?</i>

18:48.044 --> 18:51.131
That new captain, he just
doesn't understand your dad.

18:51.214 --> 18:54.843
