him he couldn't bring animals into the, uh-

18:54.926 --> 18:56.719
into the office anymore.

18:56.803 --> 19:02.308
<i>Most people don't stop to consider that four
out of five murder victims are pet owners.</i>

19:02.392 --> 19:06.980
Your dad can't seem to manage leaving
the scene without those animals.

19:07.063 --> 19:10.108
