20:32.148 --> 20:36.069
<i>They say that</i>
<i>the apple doesn't fall far from the tree.</i>

20:36.152 --> 20:38.738
<i>I found this puzzling</i>
<i>and couldn't stop wondering-</i>

20:38.821 --> 20:42.033
<i>are our lives all mapped out for us?</i>

20:42.116 --> 20:45.912
<i>Would my daughter grow up</i>
<i>only to wear my shoes?</i>

20:45.995 --> 20:49.666
<i>Did my mother's life</i>
<i>create my destiny,</i>

20:49.749 --> 20:52.293
